# ZyncSpace Enterprise Guidelines

Read `.ai/AGENTS.md` and `.ai/README.md` before making changes.

## Core rules

- **Outcomes over features** - write for executives (see `.ai/content/messaging.md`)
- **Never fake** customers, metrics, testimonials, or certifications (see `.ai/content/ai-content-rules.md`)
- **Products vs Services** - keep separate (see `.ai/content/products-vs-services.md`)
- **Definition of done** - every page must pass `.ai/guidelines/definition-of-done.md`

## Site URLs

- Staging: `https://zyncspace.in` · Production: `https://zyncspace.com`
- Set via `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` at build time (see `.ai/engineering/environments.md`)

## Before shipping a page

1. Business value + CTA present
2. SEO metadata + JSON-LD
3. Typography uses design system (no inline font styles)
4. `npm run build` passes SEO audit

Full guidelines: `.ai/guidelines/enterprise-design.md`
